ATLANTIS ARSENAL:
-----------------
Two types of weapons make up the
arsenal which defends Atlantis.

Anti-Aircraft Guns
------------------
One anti-aircraft gun is
positioned at each sentry post
on either side of Atlantis. Aim
anti-aircraft shots with the
floating cross-hair sight.

